	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ad tabernas <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l632" cert="high">Alsaticas</placeName>, sicuti nuper praemonui, convenere <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l572" cert="high">Wirtemb[ergensis]</placeName> dux et 4 Guysiani fratres, dux, prior, cardinalis <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l691" cert="high">Lotharingius</placeName>, cardinalis <persName type="citizen_name">Guysanus</persName>.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Adduxit secum <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l572" cert="high">Wirtemb[ergensis]</placeName> <persName ref="p458" cert="high">Brentium</persName> et <persName type="auto_name">Ioannem Andreae</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Colloqu[u]ti sunt hi diu cum cardinali Lotharingio, cui commendata est ab illis confessio <placeName ref="l18" cert="high">Augustana</placeName> et confessio <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l572" cert="high">Wirtemb[ergensis]</placeName> superioribus annis oblata concilio <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1107" cert="high">Tridentino</placeName> etc.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid concluserint, incertum; hoc autem <placeName ref="l491" cert="high">Argentina</placeName> scribitur ad me unum ex fratribus profectururm, cardinalem opinor <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l691">Lotharingium</placeName>, recta in concilium <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1107" cert="high">Tridentinum</placeName> et effecturum, ut inde legatus mittatur ad <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l822">Germanos</placeName> principes.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid ergo quaeritur nisi intestina discordia inter principes <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l822" cert="high">Germanos</placeName>, aut ut his concedatur sua illa confessio, principes vicissim defendant aut non opprimant episcopos etc.?</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Additur in literis pateras argenteas graves a card[inale] datas dono utrique; quod si verum est, profecto mirum est ministros Christi accepisse munus ab eo, qui madet adhuc sanguine martyrum Christi.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed haec ad te scribo, ut ad me sunt perlata; utcunque res habeat, video nobis maxima pericula imminere et undique nos petendos.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed fortior est, qui in nobis quam qui in mundo est.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vidisti, quae scripserit contra nos <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p20367">Hesshusius</persName>.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Oro, si statuisti respondere, respondeas ad argumenta diligenter praeterita persona illa <persName type="auto_name">Thersitis</persName> <persName type="auto_name">Homerici</persName>; idem suggerito et d. <persName ref="p8033" cert="high">Bezae</persName> nostro.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ego non minus venenata expecto a <persName ref="p458" cert="high">Brentio</persName>.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Gratificareris mihi, si scriberes tuum mihi iudicium de responsione mea, quam te accepisse spero.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Remitto d. <persName ref="p8033" cert="high">Bezae</persName> literas<note type="misc"><persName ref="p8033" cert="high">Beza</persName> an HB, 2. März [1562</note>], sicut petieras, et oro, ut, quid ab eo tempore factum sit, ad me perscribas; nihil enim prorsus audimus, nisi quod Navarrus ad papam defecerit.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus reducat illum!</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Mitto et confessionem ecclesiae <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2472" cert="high">Polonicae</placeName>, de qua nuper etiam monueram.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Literas appositas quaeso cures tradi d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8511" cert="high">Christophoro Trecio</persName> <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2472" cert="high">Polono</placeName>, quem tibi commendo, et te optime valere cupio.</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tiguri</placeName> 13. martii 1562.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Festinantissime scripsi propter abiturientem tabellionem.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Salutant te fratres.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Bullingerus</persName> tuus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro d. <persName ref="p540" cert="high">Ioanni Calvino</persName>, <placeName ref="l167" cert="high">Genevensis</placeName> ecclesiae ministro fideli, domino et fratri suo colendo et dilecto.</s>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><placeName ref="l167" cert="high">Genff</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
